text: Trump calls attention to unidentified event in Sweden Please enable flash to watch this video. Sorry, this video is not available. Your browser does not currently support live streaming video. Play Video Live Video - At a Florida rally on Feb. 18, President Trump listed several countries that have taken in large numbers of refugees and have also been recently struck by terror attacks. "Look at what is happening last night in Sweden," Trump said, "They took in large numbers. They're having problems like they never thought possible." Sweden does not know what Trump is talking about.
